abstract
--------

prototype work to integrate an avro protocol handler to netty.

contents
--------

avro mail client/server

  # server
  % java -classpath ./libs/avro-1.3.0.jar:./libs/avro-tools-1.3.0.jar:./libs/jackson-mapper-asl-1.4.0.jar:./libs/jackson-core-asl-1.4.0.jar:./libs/netty-3.1.5.GA.jar:./libs/protobuf-java-2.2.0.jar:./libs/slf4j-api-1.5.8.jar:./libs/slf4j-simple-1.5.8.jar prototype.avro.Server

  # client
  % java -classpath ./libs/avro-1.3.0.jar:./libs/avro-tools-1.3.0.jar:./libs/jackson-mapper-asl-1.4.0.jar:./libs/jackson-core-asl-1.4.0.jar:./libs/netty-3.1.5.GA.jar:./libs/protobuf-java-2.2.0.jar:./libs/slf4j-api-1.5.8.jar:./libs/slf4j-simple-1.5.8.jar prototype.avro.Client 9090 to-tammy from-james message-rocks

